{"type":"RECORD","stream":"stream_trello_cards","record":{"id":"649b690db9919de56c6c81ab","badges":{"fogbugz":"","checkItems":0,"checkItemsChecked":0,"checkItemsEarliestDue":null,"comments":0,"attachments":1,"description":true,"due":null,"dueComplete":false,"start":null,"location":false,"votes":0,"viewingMemberVoted":false,"subscribed":false},"checkItemStates":[],"closed":false,"dueComplete":false,"dateLastActivity":"2023-06-27T22:56:14.224Z","desc":"Ideas are created and share here through a card. \nHere you can describe what you'd like to accomplish.\nFor example you can follow three simple questions to create the card related to your idea:\n\n  * Why  ? (Why do you wish to do it ?)\n  * What ? (What it  is it, what are the goals, who is concerned)\n  * How  ? (How do you think you can do it ? What are the required steps ?)\n\nAfter creation, you can move your card to the todo list.","due":null,"dueReminder":null,"email":null,"idBoard":"649b690db9919de56c6c8158","idChecklists":[],"idList":"649b690db9919de56c6c815f","idMembers":[],"idMembersVoted":[],"idShort":1,"idAttachmentCover":null,"labels":[],"idLabels":[],"manualCoverAttachment":true,"name":"\u270b\ud83c\udfff Add what you'd like to work on below","pos":16384,"shortLink":"zWmtyVd4","shortUrl":"https://trello.com/c/zWmtyVd4","start":null,"subscribed":false,"url":"https://trello.com/c/zWmtyVd4/1-%E2%9C%8B%F0%9F%8F%BF-add-what-youd-like-to-work-on-below","isTemplate":false,"cardRole":null},"time_extracted":"2025-06-10T15:11:04.311258+00:00"}
