{"type":"RECORD","stream":"stream_trello_cards","record":{"id":"649b6874c302fa6013873150","badges":{"fogbugz":"","checkItems":0,"checkItemsChecked":0,"checkItemsEarliestDue":null,"comments":0,"attachments":1,"description":false,"due":null,"dueComplete":false,"start":null,"location":false,"votes":0,"viewingMemberVoted":false,"subscribed":false},"checkItemStates":[],"closed":false,"dueComplete":false,"dateLastActivity":"2023-06-27T22:53:40.783Z","desc":"","due":null,"dueReminder":null,"email":null,"idBoard":"649b6874c302fa60138730f7","idChecklists":[],"idList":"649b6874c302fa6013873101","idMembers":[],"idMembersVoted":[],"idShort":4,"idAttachmentCover":null,"labels":[],"idLabels":[],"manualCoverAttachment":true,"name":"\u270b\ud83c\udfff Move anything from doing to done here","pos":16384,"shortLink":"XoGqIHbL","shortUrl":"https://trello.com/c/XoGqIHbL","start":null,"subscribed":false,"url":"https://trello.com/c/XoGqIHbL/4-%E2%9C%8B%F0%9F%8F%BF-move-anything-from-doing-to-done-here","isTemplate":false,"cardRole":null},"time_extracted":"2025-06-10T15:11:05.149195+00:00"}
{"type":"RECORD","stream":"stream_trello_cards","record":{"id":"649b6874c302fa6013873146","badges":{"fogbugz":"","checkItems":4,"checkItemsChecked":3,"checkItemsEarliestDue":null,"comments":0,"attachments":0,"description":true,"due":null,"dueComplete":false,"start":null,"location":false,"votes":0,"viewingMemberVoted":false,"subscribed":false},"checkItemStates":[{"idCheckItem":"649b6874c302fa6013873451","state":"complete"},{"idCheckItem":"649b6874c302fa6013873452","state":"complete"},{"idCheckItem":"649b6874c302fa6013873453","state":"complete"}],"closed":false,"dueComplete":false,"dateLastActivity":"2023-06-27T22:53:40.327Z","desc":"## Why\n\n### Pain\n\nHow can members share freely ideas and follow them, team up to accomplish them ?\nA simple idea is trello board visible to everyone but only managed by members.\n\n### Users\n\n- Everyone\n\n---\n\n## What\n\nCommon board where ideas are listed.\nThe board should be public and only members can edit it.\nA board is defined as a _list_ of items.\nEach list will hold items that represent ideas.\nEach list is a stage or like a of the ideas, except for the 'labels' list holding categories of projects.\nWe can devise the following lists:\n\n- **Brainstorm**: Ideas are created here. Here people can describe the idea  following three simple questions:\n  - Why they wish to do it\n  - What it is\n  - How they wish to do it (tasks)\n- **Todo**: Once the ideas is clearly defined, the task can move to #todo stage. Here the owner of the idea can move to #doing once s/he is ready. He can also wait a bit for other members to join.\n- **Doing**: On-going\n- **Done**: Finished\n\n---\n\n## How\n\nSee subtasks list","due":null,"dueReminder":null,"email":null,"idBoard":"649b6874c302fa60138730f7","idChecklists":["649b6874c302fa6013873148"],"idList":"649b6874c302fa6013873101","idMembers":[],"idMembersVoted":[],"idShort":5,"idAttachmentCover":null,"labels":[],"idLabels":[],"manualCoverAttachment":false,"name":"Card Template \ud83d\udcdd","pos":81920,"shortLink":"UpEZ5kMI","shortUrl":"https://trello.com/c/UpEZ5kMI","start":null,"subscribed":false,"url":"https://trello.com/c/UpEZ5kMI/5-card-template-%F0%9F%93%9D","isTemplate":true,"cardRole":null},"time_extracted":"2025-06-10T15:11:05.149341+00:00"}
